{"tid":2108893,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"水煙同好會 (1)","createTime":"2020-07-15T01:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T05:07:39.000Z","uid":146574,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"877280c526ffdabeaf75c586b25387afc9a04cf5","tid":2108893,"uid":146574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T01:02:47.000Z","msg":"希望大家分享下交流下點玩佢既味道同變化<br />\n本人新手<br />\n最近太多病毒都無出去食<br />\n所以自己買左個<br />\n<br />\n我自己鍾意煙霧離漫<br />\n好大煙<br />\n但點整都整唔到<br />\n<br />\n希望大家一齊分享<br />\n<br />\n已經喺香港 日本 印尼 菲律賓 英國 <br />\n西班牙 泰國 韓國 都食過<br />\n<br />\n先講吓咁多個國家嘅感受<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港 我自己認為係最成熟嘅地方<br />\n好多地方都整得好好食<br />\n推介有 諾士佛台都OK<br />\n<br />\n日本 嗰時比女僕拉咗上嚟 好難食<br />\n<br />\n印尼  唔差 平均百零蚊  佢哋嗰邊叫做shisha caf&eacute; 係一個冇得叫酒嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓 好多女會撩你玩<br />\n<br />\n英國 好濃烈 隔離啲契弟食大麻 警察都唔會理<br />\n<br />\n西班牙 食得多好舒服 冇咩特別<br />\n<br />\n泰國 原隻西瓜整出嚟都有<br />\n<br />\n韓國不過不失 女正<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7MVBhhb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7MVBhhb.png&h=f6be3c5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HWlOMIJeRvw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHWlOMIJeRvw&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuK0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=4a9a3344\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HWlOMIJeRvw</a>"},{"pid":"4ab85e502170a08dee7bee2394c8dc5b8dba8c49","tid":2108893,"uid":136952,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T01:24:41.000Z","msg":"反而覺得諾士佛臺個邊都好一般咋喎.."},{"pid":"c825c3d93e5c226a3313fff7d13ce1037ef158db","tid":2108893,"uid":13700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T01:27:00.000Z","msg":"有無試過mono light 先？我自己覺得佢地d味mix得幾好，又多款"},{"pid":"a8ea66ea5e90417e0730cdb85f1fca76fbadc68c","tid":2108893,"uid":146574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ab85e502170a08dee7bee2394c8dc5b8dba8c49","tid":2108893,"uid":136952,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T01:24:41